Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}6 5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FENRIR, execute
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,655)}芬里尔 引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单独上没法破坏他的护壁！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们配合一下时机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上 一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手 一骑 消灭这个怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个就轮到你了 真壁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来杀了世界的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来 Mk.Nicht
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还没到结束的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位置更新
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只有你动得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去阻止流浪者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在说这个虽然迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过能够把指挥交给同伴 自己去战斗的感觉真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 美羽也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到你出生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 同化我们的憎恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么到那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的声音没有传到？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牵牛…纯粹的Mir降临了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都会被控制的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种玩意…要怎么对付啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(Partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 史彦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门发出应答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未知Mir从上空接近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们离开岛的未来也到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽把我的话带给了那个Mir
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让他在岛上入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要把它变成有益的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的力量还太弱小 做不到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你同化！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至连憎恨的理由都已经忘记的绝望的内核
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在与虚无的力量会阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内核的亡灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受到了吗 这就是疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我给予你们的祝福！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到达最充满希望的未来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后有朝一日 让这个岛再次醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把生命还给岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去迎接下一个诞生的内核吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方案Δ发布！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方案Δ发布了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,织姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立上 等等 别过去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别犹豫 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向注视未来 承受战斗 保护我们到最后一刻的龙宫岛内核——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城织姬表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有大家的希望 我才会诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alvis全员 一定会再次回到这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澄美？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来执行方案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充满全舰的岛的大气会保证你的生存
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也撑不了多长时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我想至少留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你睡着之前 我会帮你维持通信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你能和他们道别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为有拥有人心的内核
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才能活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧 真壁！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便不在了 曾经存在的证据也会留在某个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 翔子 卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完了 真壁！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心现在在哪里？光弘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把小艾…杀死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 真壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消灭我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹 你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:16:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,织姬你总是一个人偷偷地哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然伤心也一直保护着大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会永远和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹你要活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有能力改变你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可以让你沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星球上 能和你对话的人存在于未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个时刻到来之前 先在这个岛上睡下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两侧舰区出航进程开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛已进入自动潜航模式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要主任在CDC！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 快出来！求你了 妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走吧 咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和剑司一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在…就去找你 诚一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也睡吧 直到岛醒来的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见吧 芹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全体岛民
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是新的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定会再次回到故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…我们到达的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕吗 Mk.Nicht
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对自己的存在将要消失的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是苦痛的根源吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对诞生的恐惧也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦 悲伤 生存的一切都是祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,织姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当接受一切祝福世界的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都会打开充满希望的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时 那都是可以相信的未来 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回去了吗 织姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也回去吧 回到生命的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Festum的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是它的入口 存在与虚无的边界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回我应该会真正跨过这条边界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在将存在与虚无的调合托付给未来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带领大家走向未来吧 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 在彼此的祝福的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无数次重逢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是正确的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小艾和光弘也是 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道什么是正确的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以开枪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽 姐姐他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.07,0:22:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…都在这里
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED1-ep26.ver）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你保护了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.92,0:22:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:22:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到我们的岛去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,40,,{\fnMingLiU\fs40\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\3a&HFF&\fad(800,800)}— 海神岛 两年后 —
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 那对面有什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有世界和你的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界…故乡？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.07,0:23:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将会懂得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕生存充满痛苦也依旧选择存在的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让我与你相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将随着世界的祝福而不断相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.43,0:24:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无数次回到尚未得见的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.13,0:24:11.72,titlenx,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(4000,0)}苍穹的法芙娜{\fnLucida Calligraphy\b0\fs40} Dead Aggressor {\fn\fs\b}—离乡—
